{"tid":870597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉紅芒草田成網紅景點 杭州夫婦花三年心血培養　三日被踩爛","createTime":"2018-10-21T09:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T02:16:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61527fd2ea2785d3f6f17d9bb72054e5686ad6f5","tid":870597,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/170626_117c278b61cae5e7a7f49058478e7ffe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F170626_117c278b61cae5e7a7f49058478e7ffe.png&h=655f6fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/170633_ff8349ce5b05c3c9b127f27d6aef9dd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F170633_ff8349ce5b05c3c9b127f27d6aef9dd2.png&h=e49c6fe3&s={SIZE}\" />浙江杭州的一個公園，種植了一大片粉紅芒草，配上粉紅色風車，吸引了不少人來影相「打卡」，一到周末，一日內就有3000人來拍照，芒草都被踩爛了。<br />\n<br />\n負責照顧這片花田的鄭阿姨和老公，兩個人攔都攔不住。無奈之下，他們唯有將花割掉，避免人們來拍照的時候，連花根都坐爛，而割下來的粉紅芒草就送給遊客：「這個花踩到這樣了，再不割掉明年長不好，現在割掉它明年還要長得更好。沒辦法，實在沒辦法，這些人的素質也怎麼說呢。」<br />\n<br />\n這裡原本是一家婚紗公司的拍攝場地，本來計劃10月底還給當局，改造成開放式公園。芒草是他們三年前由澳洲入口，一直由鄭阿姨兩夫婦照顧，而看著心血被人踩爛，鄭阿姨和老公都生氣得病了。<br />\n<br />\n「我們花了3年時間，花了好幾萬塊錢，當時十幾萬塊錢，那個種子買來種下去。好了，今年是最好的時候，花了3年的人力物力下去後，3天就給我踩光了。」<br />\n<br />\n#辣手摧花<br />\n#花海<br />\n#質素這回事<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/980971002094968/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F980971002094968%2F&d=BqY1nZ9xAMQx3w6LkQeDmAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=b9bd7722\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/980971002094968/</a>"},{"pid":"d6106e0600737d6668f2cba34e17ea6c7c5d7125","tid":870597,"uid":171192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"85d5dec995932cb6f2c6846fffc3b3b320f48a77","tid":870597,"uid":43173,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/02/10/20/01D974B40000044D-3441036-image-a-1_1455137354089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F02%2F10%2F20%2F01D974B40000044D-3441036-image-a-1_1455137354089.jpg&h=65414655&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf8bcf7cab8224f55ece032d25df06590116329d","tid":870597,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:02:22.000Z","msg":"蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7529c039f25d8422fd516ba18f4bdc30209ce2f4","tid":870597,"uid":103513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:19:59.000Z","msg":"身為中國人都唔知中國人質素係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baa9567fae8bb527f6cf6ee12411fa2f8268f66","tid":870597,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}